data.description: Great bones! Priced accordingly, this 3 bdrm, 1 bath split level house awaits someone to love and update to make their own. An addition enlarged the LR and DR but house boasts original kitchen with retro metal cabinets, 3 sizable bedrooms with HDWD flrs, full original bath. The lower level hosts a family room and laundry room/work room with doors accessing both front and back yards. Step out of the kitchen into a screened in porch - perfect for relaxing or entertaining. This house offers a blank palate for the right buyer. Large corner fenced in level lot. House is in a flood plain and requires flood insurance.
